title: Mining Active / AFK (Warrior) 100+
comment_one: Max Brute Efficiency, Health Booster, Fist Of Rage and Idle Skilling in that order. Any left over points can go into LUK.
comment_two: Max Copper Collector, Tool Proficiency, Big Pick, Motherlode Miner and Tempestuous Emotions in that order.
comment_three: Max Back to Basics, Strongest Statues and STR Summore in that order. If you are using Obols with STR and have left over points, level Fistful of Obol as well.
